snippet.title: Shattered Heaven - First Look with Game Director
snippet.description:
A playthrough of the very first dungeon of Shattered Heaven.
Discover the basics of the game with Game Director Giacomo Masi.

Pledge now on KICKSTARTER for exclusive rewards!

KICKSTARTER: https://bit.ly/ShatteredHeavenKickstarter

WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM:  https://bit.ly/ShatteredHeavenSteam
